88\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 8.014321895379676e-13, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anti-transgender activists\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"right-wing politicians\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's victory\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snopespreviously published a detailed story debunking the rumor.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a detailed story\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"the rumor\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Separately inMarchandMay2025, however, posts appeared online alleging that theWorld Boxing Organization (WBO), a different sanctioning body, had banned Khelif from competing in its events for life and stripped her of prize money and of her medals because she's a man.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5570277273345473e-15, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Separately inMarchandMay2025\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"posts\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"WBO\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"a different sanctioning body\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"its events\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"her medals\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The claim was false - World Boxing Organization PresidentGustavo Olivieri told Snopes via email that the WBO was not responsible for sanctioning amateur boxing (also called Olympic-style boxing) fights.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snopes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snopes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snopes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snopes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The claim\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"false - World Boxing Organization PresidentGustavo Olivieri\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"email\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the WBO\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"amateur boxing\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic-style boxing\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"fights\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the WBO only sanctioned professional boxing matches.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"score\": 0.9995328928631171, \"rank\": 0.00046732542815036487, \"text\": \"WBO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professional boxing matches\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Accordingly, any claims suggesting that the WBO has imposed a ban on amateur boxers are patently false,\\\" Olivieri wrote.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"score\": 0.9995328928631171, \"rank\": 0.00046732542815036487, \"text\": \"WBO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any claims\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"a ban\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"amateur boxers\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"Olivieri\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The WBO does not oversee amateur boxing, nor does it have the authority to regulate or restrict the participation of amateur athletes in non-professional competitions.\\\"\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"score\": 0.9995328928631171, \"rank\": 0.00046732542815036487, \"text\": \"WBO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amateur boxing\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"the authority\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the participation\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"amateur athletes\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"non-professional competitions\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The response echoed anOctober 2024 news releasefrom the WBO, which said the organization \\\"had not tested, nor had it banned female boxer Imane Khelif.\\\"\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r